2. Product Vision & Goals
Vision Statement:
"Redefining Plant Care as a Wellness Experience Through Intelligent Connection with Nature"
Primary Goals:
Enable plants to â€œcommunicateâ€ their needs in a conscious, emotionally resonant way.


